<div class="card-header">
<h1>Funding Plan</h1>

  <strong>Business Idea:</strong>
  <%# link_to @funding_plan.business_idea.title, @funding_plan.business_idea %>
</div>
<div class="card-body">
<div id="<%= dom_id funding_plan %>">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <div class="card my-3">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="card-title"><h3 class="text-border-radius-2xl">Bank loan borrowing:</h3></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <%= format_text_to_html(funding_plan.bank_loan_borrowing) %>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <%= button_to "Generate AI Answer for Bank Loan", generate_ai_funding_plan_path(@funding_plan, field: "bank_loan"), method: :post, class: "btn btn-outline-primary mb-5" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="card-title"><h3 class="text-border-radius-2xl">Alternative funding:</h3></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <%= format_text_to_html funding_plan.alternative_funding %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <%= button_to "Generate AI Answer for Alternative Funding", generate_ai_funding_plan_path(@funding_plan, field: "alternative"), method: :post, class: "btn btn-outline-primary" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
    

</div>

<hr>

<h2>1.2.1. Bank Loan Borrowing</h2>
<p>Explain how you would secure a £25,000 bank loan and repay it using the 5 Cs of Credit:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Character:</strong> Your reputation</li>
  <li><strong>Capacity:</strong> Your financial ability to repay</li>
  <li><strong>Capital:</strong> The funds or assets you own to support your business</li>
  <li><strong>Collateral:</strong> The security you can offer</li>
  <li><strong>Conditions:</strong> How economic or industry trends could affect your ability to make repayments</li>
</ul>

<div class="mb-4 p-3 border rounded bg-light">
  <%= format_text_to_html(@funding_plan.bank_loan_borrowing.presence) || "Not generated yet." %>
</div>

<%= button_to "Generate AI Answer for Bank Loan", generate_ai_funding_plan_path(@funding_plan, field: "bank_loan"), method: :post, class: "btn btn-primary mb-5" %>

<hr>

<h2>1.2.2. Alternative Business Funding</h2>
<p>Discuss one alternative funding source instead of a £25,000 bank loan to support your business. Explain:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Why this funding source could be a better option for your business</li>
  <li>Its advantages and disadvantages</li>
</ul>

<div class="mb-4 p-3 border rounded bg-light">
  <%=format_text_to_html(@funding_plan.alternative_funding.presence) || "Not generated yet." %>
</div>

<%= button_to "Generate AI Answer for Alternative Funding", generate_ai_funding_plan_path(@funding_plan, field: "alternative"), method: :post, class: "btn btn-primary" %>

<hr>

<%= link_to 'Edit Funding Plan', edit_funding_plan_path(@funding_plan), class: "btn btn-secondary" %> |
<%= link_to 'Back to List', funding_plans_path, class: "btn btn-link" %>

</div>